# Auth is passkey-only — the SPA has no OIDC config (see docs/operations/local-auth.md). To run the client in demo
# mode (skip the WebAuthn ceremony for UI work), start it with VITE_DEMO_MODE=1.
# Web Push (roadmap #40). Generate a VAPID key pair with: npx web-push generate-vapid-keys
# The PUBLIC key is non-secret (embedded in the PWA). The private key goes in Key Vault → credential file
# (VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY_FILE on the server). Omit both to disable push (the feature degrades gracefully).
VITE_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
